      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEACH DIAMOND (8) is a newcomer to the Michael Young yard from Victoria where she won both the Vicbred Super Series Final and Breeders Crown for the three-year-old fillies last season. Strong fresh performer winning three of four first-up attempts and she'll be ready to go off a trial win. SWEET COCO NZ (7) has won a trial since breaking at the latest appearance. May need a bit of luck negotiating this starting position but came from a similar barrier when she scored three back at Pinjarra. HEAVENLY GIPSY (9) hasn't been far away of late, beaten only 2.6m last week. Draws wide but was fourth in a G3 from this barrier last month. PUSHBUTTON ROCK (6) improved plenty for a second-up win here last start. Fitter again so can be competitive.",
